game

Class GearAllowedHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.GearAllowedHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GearVisitor

    public class GearAllowedHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements GearVisitor
    GearAllowedHandler, checks whether a gear can be added to the list before comparing with the existing list of gears.
    • Character can have maximum of 1 Head Gear, 2 Foot wears, 10 Hand Gears and no limit on Jewelry.
